{"title":"麦田与薄云","authors":["流逸"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":10,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦田与薄云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流逸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦田漾成碧绿的海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声融进氤氲的地气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"省略了装饰和伴奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可以切近地感受"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真实和灌浆的成熟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当目光沿着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗意盎然的麦梢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久久滑行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便有不期而至的薄云俯临"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那也是一种目光和含义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且受过亿万年的洗礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是绚烂之极的特殊平淡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地抚着黧黑的背脊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地浸润你的生机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地祝福你的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而当风吹动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切复归如初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你耳边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正有潺潺的渠水流着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正有伴着心律的乐曲唱着"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}